     There is a long pause over the radio as the
purple and black raptor swings over the area once
more, its large wings cupping thermals as swings
lazilly in large elipses. Then, finally, as if comming
to a desision the eagle flaps its wings as it moves
lower towards the ground.

    Myrmidon's deep voice vibrates accross the
communication channel. "Greetings Lord Hydras. I am
Myrmidon, Multi Assault Warrior." His voice has the
formulaic intonation of a newly created soldier,
straight from the stassis pod. Oddly enough though his
words contain nothing of the false provado, abject
fear, or whining ingratiation of a newly created
Predacon. Instead it contains only the calm confidence
of a soldier with a hint of arrogance, some of which
becomes a little more pronouced with his next four
words: "I await your orders." 

OOC: Keep in mind, Myrmidon is speaking accross the
old Beast wars Predacon channels. ANY of the Predacons
may be able to hear him if they choose to. 

Preston
(Myrmidon)
